metadata.name: ClicotNFT DHWC box
metadata.description: Clicöt Diamond Hand Watch Club is two collections of 5,000 unique watch NFTs (for men and women) — luxurious digital collectibles crafted on the Ethereum blockchain. Your Clicöt timepiece NFT grants access to member-only benefits, the first of which is access to THE VAULT, a safe where crypto, rewards and even a ROLEX can be unlocked by the community through roadmap activation. The first 1000 holders will also get a real physical wristwatch from our shop https://clicot.com . Join the Clicöt Diamond Hand Watch Club now and visit www.clicotnft.com for more details.
